org.libav.avcodec

Interface IPacketWrapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, IWrapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPacketWrapper, PacketWrapper

    public interface IPacketWrapper
extends IWrapper, Cloneable
    Wrapper for the AVPacket. It provides access to some of the AVPacket properties.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
